Multi-asset institutional-grade strategy combining Fibonacci retracement, multi-timeframe trend alignment, order flow analysis, and adaptive volatility regime detection. Designed for stocks, precious metals (gold, silver, miners), crypto, and forex.

━━━ HOW IT WORKS ━━━

The strategy operates on a 7-layer confluence engine:

① FIBONACCI RETRACEMENT — Automatically detects significant swing highs/lows using ATR-filtered pivot detection. Calculates dynamic 38.2%, 50%, and 61.8% retracement levels with visual zone fills between levels. Entries trigger on confirmed bounce (bullish wick or green close above level) at Fib support in upswings, or rejection candle at Fib resistance in downswings.

② MULTI-TIMEFRAME FILTER — Higher timeframe (default 4H) trend confirmation via EMA crossover. Trades are only taken in the direction of the dominant trend. Prevents counter-trend entries that statistically underperform.

③ MA RIBBON (8 MAs) — Fibonacci-sequenced moving average ribbon (8, 13, 21, 34, 55, 89, 144, 233). When 6+ of 7 pairs are aligned, the ribbon confirms strong directional momentum. Supports EMA, SMA, and HMA modes.

④ ORDER FLOW — Intraday VWAP with 3 standard deviation bands. Cumulative Volume Delta (CVD) identifies hidden buying/selling pressure divergences. Volume ratio analysis detects institutional accumulation/distribution.

⑤ VOLATILITY REGIME — Bollinger Band width expansion/contraction + ATR percentile ranking. Automatically switches between trend-following mode (high volatility) and mean-reversion mode (low volatility). Adapts stop distances to current market conditions.

⑥ BREAKOUT + MEAN REVERSION — Dual-mode execution: breakout entries on new highs/lows with volume confirmation, and BB + RSI mean reversion entries during ranging conditions.

⑦ RISK MANAGEMENT — ATR-based dynamic stop loss and take profit. Optional trailing stop. Kelly Criterion position sizing calculated from live win rate and payoff ratio.

━━━ MARKETS & TIMEFRAMES ━━━

▸ Stocks — US equities, ETFs (SPY, QQQ, AAPL, TSLA, etc.)
▸ Precious Metals — XAU/USD, XAG/USD, GLD, SLV, NEM, GOLD, AEM, miners
▸ Crypto — BTC/USD, ETH/USD, SOL/USD, and all major pairs
▸ Forex — All major and cross pairs
▸ Indices — NQ, ES, YM, DAX, FTSE
▸ Commodities — Oil, Natural Gas, Copper

Recommended timeframes: 15M (scalping/intraday), 1H (swing), 4H (position).
The MTF filter automatically reads higher timeframes regardless of chart TF.

━━━ DASHBOARD ━━━

Compact 3-column light-theme dashboard (bottom right) showing:
• MTF alignment (15M / 1H / 4H) with directional arrows and score
• MA Ribbon status and alignment count
• ADX strength + Order Flow direction
• Live Fibonacci levels with prices
• Support / Resistance levels
• Stop Loss / Take Profit / Risk:Reward ratio
• Kelly % position sizing
• Confluence score (0–5) with strength label
• Session detection (London / New York / Asia / Overlap)
• Signal: ◆ LONG / ◆ SHORT / — WAIT

━━━ VISUAL FEATURES ━━━

• Fibonacci zones rendered as dashed lines with semi-transparent linefill shading between 38.2–50% and 50–61.8% levels
• Price labels at each Fib level on the right edge
• Swing high/low reference lines (dotted)
• Extension target level for take-profit reference
• Diamond-shaped entry signals (green/red)
• Subtle Fib bounce/rejection triangle markers
• Background pulse highlight on signal bars
• Gradient trend candles (RSI-based color intensity)
• Dynamic S/R lines with labels
• TP/SL lines when in position

━━━ SETTINGS ━━━

All parameters are fully configurable:
• Swing detection sensitivity (lookback, min ATR size)
• Fib levels toggle (38.2 / 50 / 61.8), zone width, bounce wick threshold
• MTF timeframe and EMA lengths
• Ribbon MA type (EMA/SMA/HMA) and alignment threshold
• Order Flow CVD period and threshold, VWAP bands
• Volatility expansion/contraction thresholds
• Breakout period, BB period, RSI levels
• SL/TP ATR multipliers, trailing stop
• ADX threshold, volume filter
• Time session filter
• All visual elements can be toggled on/off

━━━ NOTES ━━━

• This is a strategy (not indicator) — full backtest results available in Strategy Tester
• No repainting — all signals use barstate.isconfirmed
• Commission and slippage included in backtest (0.1% commission, 3 ticks slippage)
• Pine Script v6 compatible
• Pyramiding disabled by default (1 position at a time)


